news.title: NCLT sets aside Syska LED Light insolvency process as company, lender settles matter
news.para: Syska LED Lights is part of the Pune-based SSK Group, an exclusive distributor of Samsung mobiles, accessories and tables for five states in Western India.

news.title: Signature Global (India) posts net profit of Rs 41.25 crore in Q4 FY24
news.para: Signature Global (India) board has approved the investment of Rs. 34.74 crore in the 3,47,49,900 equity shares of Rs 10 each of Gurugram Commercity for cash at par.

news.title: Brookfield India Real Estate Trust to acquire 50% stake in four Bharti Enterprises assets
news.para: The acquisition by Brookfield India Real Estate Trust includes commercial properties totalling 3.3 million sq ft, at an enterprise value of c. Rs 60,000 million.

news.title: Spain's ACS net profit rise by 16% in Q1 2024
news.para: The company booked a net attributable profit of 177 million euros ($191.11 million), above the average of analysts' expectations of 172.5 million euros in an LSEG survey.

news.title: Home Depot sales drop more than expected as wary customers delay big projects
news.para: Customers have slashed discretionary spending and put pricey renovations on hold as they adjust to higher borrowing costs and elevated inflation, leading to a turbulent 2023 for home improvement retailers like Home Depot and Lowe's Cos.

news.title: Germany's PBB reports $31.27 million profit in Q1 2024
news.para: The bank's quarterly profit was 29 million euros ($31.27 million), compared with 27 million a year earlier, while provisions for loan losses shot up to 47 million euros from 2 million euros last year, it said on Tuesday.

news.title: Irish builders issue 17,600 commencement notices for homes in April
news.para: Housing has been the number one political issue for years in Ireland. A severe shortage of affordable housing has pushed rents to record highs with house prices growing at a rate of 6.1% year-on-year, despite a jump in borrowing costs.

news.title: Aadhar Housing Finance shares ends over 5% higher on debut
news.para: On the BSE, the stock made its debut at Rs 314.30, a dip of 0.22 per cent from the issue price. In intra-day, it climbed 8.95 per cent to Rs 343.20. Later, it ended at Rs 329.55 each share, up 4.61 per cent.

news.title: Government proposes holding builders, brokers responsible for unsolicited calls
news.para: Government proposes measures to crack down on pesky calls by holding entities accountable for contacting people through unregistered numbers.

news.title: Big-name funds pile into real estate debt as banks retreat
news.para: U.S. fund firms PGIM, LaSalle and Nuveen, Canada's Brookfield and QuadReal, Britain's M&G, Schroders and Aviva, and France's AXA all told Reuters they plan to increase their credit exposure to property.

news.title: DHFL scam: CBI arrests Dheeraj Wadhawan in Rs 34,000-crore bank fraud case
news.para: The CBI has arrested former DHFL Director Dheeraj Wadhawan in connection with the alleged defrauding of a 17-member lender bank consortium to the tune of Rs 34,000 crore, officials said Tuesday.

news.title: Oberoi Realty's net profit up 64.07% in Q4 FY24
news.para: Oberoi Realty's net consolidated total income stood at Rs 1,558.56 crore in Q4 FY24, a growth of 56.62 per cent from Rs 995.11 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Bajaj Electricals' net profit down 43.4% to Rs 29 crore in Q4 FY24
news.para: Consolidated total revenue from operations in the quarter under review was Rs 1,188.08 crore as compared to Rs 1,291.97 crore in the same period a year ago, it added.

news.title: Home prices in New Zealand fall by 2.1% in April 2024
news.para: Seasonally adjusted median house prices dipped 2.1% from March but were up 2.6% from a year earlier, continuing a trend seen in recent months, REINZ data showed.

news.title: Banks in Hong Kong face credit risks from property downturn: Report
news.para: With over half of their total loan portfolios tied to real estate, Hong Kong banks are heavily exposed to the property sector through lending for property development, investment, and residential mortgages, the report said.

news.title: Repco Home Finance's net profit up 31.63% in Q4 FY24
news.para: Repco Home Finance's net consolidated total income stood at Rs 397.19 crore in Q4 FY24, a growth of 15.55 per cent from Rs 343.73 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: China's Agile Group misses interest payment on $483 million offshore note
news.para: The grace period for the interest payment on the $483 million 6.05% senior notes due 2025, issued in November 2020, had expired on Monday.

news.title: Spain’s Ferrovial reports 37.6% rise in earnings in Q1 2024
news.para: Ferrovial's adjusted earnings before interest, taxes, depreciation and amortisation (EBITDA) reached 254 million euros ($274.02 million), in line with average analysts' expectations of 253.4 million euros.

news.title: Shree Cement's net profit increases by 21.15% in Q4 FY24
news.para: Shree Cement's net consolidated total income stood at Rs 5,238.88 crore in Q4 FY24, a growth of 6.47 per cent from Rs 4,920.38 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.
